overview.en: SADT is a business platform passport for small and medium-sized enterprises based on block chain technology. It is committed to helping enterprises transform and upgrade digitally through SADT. SADT provides users with: block chain SaaS solutions and commercial solutions.
overview.zh: SADT是一个基于区块链技术的中小企业商务平台通证，致力于通过SADT助力企业数字化转型升级。SADT为用户提供：区块链SaaS解决方案和商业解决方案。
